OL,5, Energy companies have been asked to    
OL,6, suspend the forced installation of     
OL,7, prepayment meters by the energy        
OL,8, regulator Ofgem.                       
OL,10,FThis comes after The Times found debt  
OL,11,Fagents for British Gas broke into      
OL,12,Fvulnerable people's homes to fit       
OL,13,Fmeters.                                
OL,15,FOfgem has asked all suppliers to review
OL,16,Fthe use of court warrants to enter the 
OL,17,Fhomes of customers in arrears.         
OL,19,FIt said firms must get their "house in 
OL,20,Forder".                                
